quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,"“Did I not enjoin on you, O you children of Adam, that you should not worship Satan, and that he was to you a sworn enemy"
  36,61,"“And that you should worship Me, and that this is the straight way"
  36,62,“But he led astray a great multitude of you. Did you not then use reason
  36,63,“This is the hell about which you were warned
  36,64,"“Embrace the fire this day, because you rejected it.”"
  36,65,"That day will We put a seal on their mouths, but their hands will speak to Us, and their feet will bear witness to all that they did"
  36,66,"If it had been Our will, We could surely have removed their eyes, then they would have run about grabbing for the path, but how could they have seen"
  36,67,"And if it had been Our will, We could have transformed them in their places, then they would have been unable to proceed, and they could not have returned"
  36,68,"If We grant long life to any, We cause them to be reversed in creation. Will they not then understand"
  36,69,"We have not instructed the messenger in poetry, nor is that like him. This is no less than a message and a Quran making things clear"
  36,70,"That it may give advice to any that are alive, and that the charge may be proven against those who reject it"
  36,71,"Do they not see that it is We who have created for them livestock, among the things that Our hands have fashioned that are under their control"
  36,72,"And that We have subjected them to their use? Of them, some carry them and some they eat"
  36,73,"And they obtain other benefits from them, including drink. Will they not then be grateful"
  36,74,"Yet they take for worship gods other than God, thinking that they might be helped"
  36,75,"They do not have the power to help them, but they will be brought up all together"
  36,76,But do not let their speech grieve you. Indeed We know what they hide as well as what they disclose
  36,77,"Do human beings not see that it is We Who created them from a zygote? Yet behold, he stands up as an open adversary"
  36,78,"And he makes comparisons to Us, and forgets his own origin and creation. He says, “Who can give life to bones, and decomposed ones at that?”"
  36,79,"Say, “He will give them life Who created them the first time. For He is well-versed in every kind of creation"
  36,80,"“The same One who produces for you fire out of the green tree, when behold, you kindle with it"
  36,81,"“Is not He Who created the heavens and the earth able to create the likes of him?” Yes indeed, for He is the Ultimate Creator, the All Knowing"
  36,82,"Indeed, when He intends a thing, His command is “Be”, and it is"
  36,83,"So glory be to Him in Whose hands are the control of all things, and to Him will you all be brought back"
  37,1,By those who line themselves in ranks
  37,2,And so are strong in repelling harm
  37,3,And so proclaim the message
  37,4,Indeed your God is one
  37,5,"Lord of the heavens and of the earth, and all between them, and Lord of every point at the rising of the Sun"
  37,6,We have indeed decked the lower heaven with beauty in the stars
  37,7,For beauty and to guard against all rebellious devils
  37,8,"They should not strain their ears in the direction of the exalted assembly, but shall be cast away from every side"
  37,9,"Repulsed, for they are under a perpetual penalty"
  37,10,"Except those that snatch away something by stealth, and they are pursued by a flaming fire of piercing brightness"
  37,11,"Just ask their opinion. Are they more difficult to create, or the other beings We have created? We have created them out of wet clay"
  37,12,Indeed you marvel while they ridicule
  37,13,"And though they are advised, they pay no heed"
  37,14,"And when they see a sign, they turn it into mockery"
  37,15,"And say, “This is nothing but evident deception"
  37,16,"“What, when we die and become dust and bones, will we be raised up"
  37,17,“And also our ancestors?”
  37,18,"Say, “Yes, and you will then be humiliated.”"
  37,19,"Then there will be a single cry, and behold, they will begin to see"
  37,20,"They will say, “Woe to us, this is the Day of Accountability!”"
  37,21,"This is the day of sorting out, the truth you once denied"